OL,3,CLife sentence given to 80 year old man
OL,4,Cfor murdering his neighbour
OL,6,FAn 80-year-old man, who murdered his
OL,7,Fneighbour with a hammer and a knife,
OL,8,Fhas been handed a life sentence.
OL,10,FPeter Kindell, of Silverdale Close in
OL,11,FAylesbury, had a long-running dispute
OL,12,Fwith his neighbour 76-year-old John
OL,13,FJones.
OL,15,FOn 3 January 2025, Kindell attacked
OL,16,Fthe 76-year-old with a hammer in the
OL,17,Flobby of his block of flats.
OL,19,FTwo women intervened to help Mr Jones
OL,20,Fand provide him with care, which led
OL,21,Fto the attacker leaving the scene.
