OL,3,CLife sentence given to 80 year old man
OL,4,Cfor murdering his neighbour
OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer Detective
OL,7,FInspector Nick Hind, from the Major
OL,8,FCrime Unit, said: "John Jones was a
OL,9,Fmuch loved man, and his loss has
OL,10,Fdevastated his family and his friends.
OL,12,F"Kindell's actions are beyond
OL,13,Fcomprehension and there can be no
OL,14,Fexcuses for what he did. The intent
OL,15,Fand level of violence which he
OL,16,Finflicted on John was ferocious in
OL,17,Fnature, and Kindell has now been held
OL,18,Ffully accountable and sentenced to
OL,19,Flife imprisonment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
